Scenario 1: Booking a ride

Given that I have the Inficab app installed and my location services are enabled,
When I open the app,
Then I should see a map interface with my current location pinpointed.
Scenario 2: Entering destination

Given that I am on the map interface,
When I tap on the search bar and enter my destination,
Then the app should provide autocomplete suggestions for destinations.
Scenario 3: Selecting a ride

Given that I have entered my destination,
When I select a type of vehicle (e.g., sedan, SUV, luxury),
Then the app should display the estimated fare and time of arrival for each option.
Scenario 4: Confirming the ride

Given that I have chosen my preferred ride option,
